    "Generally traditional ML models often do not incorporate any prior knowledge about the physical system they are modeling.",
    "Ns, on the other hand, are designed to incorporate physical laws and equations that govern the system as a part of the NN architecture.",
    "This is one of the key advantages when applying PINN based ML models to complex, physics-based applications such as a power system.",
    "There are several reasons why PINNs could be particularly useful for power system protection applications.",
    "The most important advantage is that improved generalizability."
